Internet Download Manager 6.25
1]. Run idman625.exe to install the program. 2]. Exit program from system tray. (It is Important). 3]. Copy IDMan.exe from folder 'Patch' into the installation folder of IDM and confirm replacing. 4]. Open keygen.exe and click on generate and copy the key. 5]. Register the IDM with the generated key. 6]. Run the program and enjoy!!!.
